title: Need a verifiable way to confirm updated workspace docs are injected on subsequent turns
---
The assistant can write active workspace files like AGENTS.md and reasonably expect them to be injected into subsequent turns, but from inside a running session it cannot directly verify the exact hidden system prompt contents. We need either a trustworthy runtime guarantee or an introspection/debug path that confirms which workspace docs and revisions were injected for a given turn. This matters for prompt-operating-system edits such as AGENTS.md autonomy rules.